<p>I am a user experience researcher and strategic designer. I help companies understand their customers in greater depth, identifying unmet needs and new opportunities.</p> 

<p>I prototype visions of the future, and shape new digital products and services. I believe in putting people and their needs at the heart of innovation. I work with with strategic design studio <a href="http://www.monoko.to">Monokoto</a>.</p> 